Global Lemon-flavored Tablets Market Insights
Lemon-flavored Tablets Market size was valued at USD 1.2 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 2.5 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 10.0% from 2024 to 2030.

Lemon-flavored Tablets Market Overview
The lemon-flavored tablets market has experienced significant growth, primarily driven by the increasing demand for dietary supplements, throat lozenges, and convenience-based health products. The market value in 2023 was estimated to be around USD 2.3 billion and is expected to grow at a CAGR of 7.5% from 2024 to 2030. The surge in demand for lemon-flavored tablets in various applications, such as vitamin supplements and cough syrups, has been crucial in shaping the market dynamics. Additionally, the growing preference for natural and refreshing flavors further drives the market's expansion.

